data.description: Welcome to 4580 Willow Croft Dr! This spacious 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home boasts 2036 sqft of living space and offers a lifestyle of convenience and luxury. The Condo fee covers many amenities such as internet, phone, cable, pool access, clubhouse access, grounds maintenance, and trash pickup, ensuring a hassle-free lifestyle for residents. Nestled in a beautiful and quiet neighborhood, this home offers tranquility while still being close to shopping centers, major interstates, and naval bases, providing easy access to all the amenities Virginia Beach has to offer. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make 4580 Willow Croft Dr your new home. Schedule a showing today and experience the best of Virginia Beach!
